sort1=sorting zone on left side
sort2=sorting zone on right side

upper_left_1=upper left terminal on left side
upper_left_2=upper left terminal on right side

others are analogue of this.

Enjoy!!


sort1_upper_left_1(){

	left_turn();
	blackline();
	right_turn();
	

}
sort2_upper_left_1(){
	left_turn();
	blackline();
	letf_turn();
	blackline();
}

